    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Female Coeliccia spp. used for description. (a) C. galbina, habitus; (b) C. hayashii, head and thorax in hand in dorsolateral view; (c) C. hayashii, in hand; (d) C. suoitia, scan, freshly dead." ;
